{"id":"172338516139198_1399483123424725","from":{"name":"Mohamed Gamal","id":"10155052545932328"},"message":"SA,\nI'm generating reports from mySQL db. The report counts, takes average, etc.. from multiple tables and columns. (Note that count, avr, etc.. returns a table with one row)\nI want to concatinate these one row tables in one table.\nIt's like UNION but done horizontally not vertically.\n\nAny suggestions?","actions":[{"name":"Comment","link":"https://www.facebook.com/172338516139198/posts/1399483123424725"},{"name":"Like","link":"https://www.facebook.com/172338516139198/posts/1399483123424725"},{"name":"Report Post to Admin","link":"https://www.facebook.com/groups/egyptian.geeks/members/"}],"privacy":{"value":"","description":"","friends":"","allow":"","deny":""},"type":"status","created_time":"2017-02-24T15:29:54+0000","updated_time":"2017-02-25T15:15:34+0000","is_hidden":false,"is_expired":false,"comments":{"data":[{"created_time":"2017-02-24T15:40:30+0000","from":{"name":"Osama Soliman","id":"709206249239999"},"message":"may this help ?\nhttps://www.w3schools.com/sql/sql_join.asp","can_remove":false,"like_count":0,"user_likes":false,"id":"1399488563424181"},{"created_time":"2017-02-24T17:20:22+0000","from":{"name":"Tarek Moukhtar","id":"10154129433586650"},"message":"Simple select for each column. Poor in performance. U can replace it for maintainability by functions.","can_remove":false,"like_count":0,"user_likes":false,"id":"1399568530082851"},{"created_time":"2017-02-24T17:52:59+0000","from":{"name":"Mohammed Farghal","id":"10154511379887689"},"message":"select (query1) as average, (query2) as count...etc\n\nExample:\nselect (select count(*) from table1) as cnt, (select avg(col) from table2) as average;\n\nthis will give you a table having one row with 2 columns (cnt, average)","can_remove":false,"like_count":1,"user_likes":false,"id":"1399598746746496"},{"created_time":"2017-02-25T04:36:52+0000","from":{"name":"Essam Abd Ellatif Essawy","id":"1453319